{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710890/extras/GIF_UNWELL_12_10_small_02.gif?t=1737487244\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game about a troubled mind succumbing to the calls of the void.</strong> </h2>Will it endure it's last stand against The Gray? <br><br>Traverse the troubled depths of human psyche with caution. Sometimes the most perilous adversary of the mind is its own consciousness. <br>Choose your way of dealing with the troubled mind adversaries. <br>Hide, distract or fight back.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Seek the way down.</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710890/extras/c.gif?t=1737487244\" /><br><br>Use the twisted environment to your advantage. Seek refuge.<br>Even a simple stone can save your life. Throw it to redirect unwanted interest of other well dwellers. <br>But when cornered... fight back.<br>Explore the depths to find clues, overcome obstacles and solve puzzles to unravel the mysteries of the well.<br><br><strong>Unwell</strong> is an isometric survival horror game with a narrative inspired by the psychological theory of personality by Sigmund Freud and The Map Of Consciousness by David R. Hawkins.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710890/extras/b.gif?t=1737487244\" /><br><br>Unwell is a story that hits close to home, experienced in a twisted way. The themes manifested in the game will concern each and every one of us. Sooner or later. <br>In one way or another.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737487244","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710890/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737487244","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710890/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737487